A cozy home office desk viewed from above in Studio Ghibli style, featuring an open laptop displaying a friendly penguin mascot on screen, surrounded by scattered CD cases with colorful disc artwork, a steaming cup of tea, and warm afternoon sunlight streaming through a window with potted plants on the sill. The scene has soft watercolor textures, gentle pastel colors with warm orange and teal accents, and that characteristic Ghibli sense of peaceful domesticity. A small cat curiously peers at the laptop screen from the corner of the desk. The atmosphere conveys the excitement of exploration and new beginnings, with gentle dust motes floating in the sunbeam.
